B.a0X=new A.af("Army Connect Pro Privacy Policy\n\nData Collection:\nWe collect only necessary data for app functionality including:\n- Anonymous user identification\n- Chat messages and images\n- Member information (admin only)\n\nData Usage:\nYour data is used solely for:\n- Providing real-time messaging\n- Member management\n- App functionality\n\nData Security:\nAll data is encrypted and stored securely on Firebase servers.\nWe do not share your data with third parties.\n\nContact:\nFor privacy concerns, contact the app administrator.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
